<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77a612d8-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s450jj–10"><num value="450jj–10">§ 450jj–10.</num><heading> Designation of Gateway Arch National Park</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id77a612d9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s450jj–10/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> Redesignation</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Jefferson National Expansion Memorial established under sections 450jj to 450jj–9 of this title shall be known and designated as the “Gateway Arch National Park”.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id77a612da-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s450jj–10/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> References</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Any reference in a law, map, regulation, document, paper, or other record of the United States to the Jefferson National Expansion Memorial shall be considered to be a reference to the “Gateway Arch National Park”.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id77a612db-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/115/128/s2">Pub. L. 115–128, § 2</ref>, <date date="2018-02-22">Feb. 22, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/328">132 Stat. 328</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
